name: Mara Nobody
description:
THE FIRST AND ORIGINAL NOBODY (fake consistent character)

Follow me to make sure you see new styles, poses and Nobodys when I post them. Things move fast on this site, it's easy to miss.

Meet Mara Nobody, this person doesn't exist. You may think she looks like someone you know, but she isn't. Just the imprecise nature of diffusion. Stylized images created by the legendary A to Zovya RPG Artist's Tools model.

If you need a consistent character but don't want a known celebrity, Mara is your gal. It's a strong embedding and she loves to have long blonde hair and pretty dresses unless you turn down the strength.

Follow me for more of the Nobody family coming soon for 1.5 and 2.1.
Click the zNobody tag for more, or the Nobody tag to see other's contributions.

Do you have requests? I've been putting in many more hours lately with this. That's my problem, not yours. But if you'd like to tip me, buy me a beer. Beer encourages me to ignore work and make AI models instead. Tip and make a request. I'll give it a shot if I can. Here at Ko-Fi
